name: Nyubuna Bulul

attributes.name: Affiliation(s)
values: The Even Cut Sabacc Parlor and Casino

content: Nyubuna Bulul was a female Mon Calamari and the owner of The Even Cut Sabacc Parlor and Casino, in the Center Sphere District of Bartyn's Landing  as of 29 BBY. Bulul had skill for business and was the direct competitor to Miss Mylla, with their businesses being neighbors to each other.
